{"title":"在沙漠度过夏天","authors":["林染"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":9,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在沙漠度过夏天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林染"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨，走出帐篷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遂为塔里木瀚海所包围"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难得无风的天气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空如盛着净水的陶罐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是瓦蓝色的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但沙漠实在干燥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十点钟以后，每颗沙砾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竞争着炽烈起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连飞鸟也难得问津的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而他将和他的铝盔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和工装口袋中一个姑娘的彩照"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里度过夏天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上岗，朝钻机走去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻机如他的青春的臂膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正执拗地进尺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深入岩层"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石油钻机隐约的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在荒原上美丽而孤单"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再悄悄看一眼彩照上的女友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不禁温柔地想起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻台上那盆皇后月季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又该浇水了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：甘肃酒泉《阳关》编辑部）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}